{{rfd}}
==English==
===Interogative phrase===
'''[[do]]/[[does]]''' ''one'''''?'''

# ''[[request|Request]] for [[confirmation]] that converts a negative present tense sentence into a [[question]]. Expects [[agreement]] in a "no" answer.''
#:<tt>“</tt>You don't expect me to go in there, '''do you'''?<tt>”</tt>
#:<tt>“</tt>Jessica doesn't have a pet lizzard, '''does she'''?<tt>”</tt>

====Usage notes====
Number distinguishes ''do'' versus ''does''.

===Tag===
'''does [[one]]?'''
# ''Request for confirmation (as above).''
#:<tt>“</tt>One doesn't use the indefinite personal pronoun often, '''does one'''?<tt>”</tt>

===Antonyms===
* [[doesn't one?]]
* [[does one not?]]

